---
title: Cheesy Pumpkin & Chilli-Rosemary Gratin with Rocket & Cucumber Salad
description: Sweet and savoury roast pumpkin? Check. A golden, herby crumb? Check. An ooey gooey creamy sauce holding everything together? Check! This gratin has it all and then some, perfectly balanced out with a fresh rocket salad. This veggie wonder will appeal to even the biggest carnivores.
